NVIDIA AI Enterprise Production Branch October Updates.<p><strong>Productio=
n Branch October 2025 - Now available to NVIDIA AI Enterprise Subscribers</=
strong><br><br>Production Branch October 2025 contains specific versions of=
 AI frameworks, SDKs and selected NVIDIA NIM microservices that are guarant=
eed to maintain API stability across monthly security updates, and provide =
a secure and stable environment for building AI applications.<br><br><stron=
g>Government Ready Images Now Included</strong><br><br>Certain x86 containe=
r images within the Production Branch October 2025 release are designated a=
s Government Ready Software. These specific hardened images meet the string=
ent security requirements of highly regulated industries, including governm=
ent and sovereign environments (e.g., FedRAMP High and equivalent sovereign=
 environments).<br><br>Download Production Branch October 2025 from the <a =
href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nvidia/collections/production_b=
ranch_october_2025" rel=3D"nofollow">Production Branch October 2025 Collect=
ion</a> on the NGC Catalog.</p>
<p>Several new Infrastructure 7 Release software containers also satisfy go=
vernment-ready requirements and can be accessed through the <a href=3D"http=
s://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nvidia/collections/nvidia-ai-enterprise-inf=
ra-7" rel=3D"nofollow">NVIDIA AI Enterprise Infra 7 Collection</a>.<br><br>=
Learn more about Production Branch in the <a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.co=
m/ai-enterprise/release-notes/latest/production-branch.html#production-bran=
ch-may-2025-pb-25h2" rel=3D"nofollow">Production Branch release notes</a> a=
nd the <a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/ai-enterprise/planning-resource/r=
elease-branches/latest/release-branches.html#" rel=3D"nofollow">NVIDIA AI E=
nterprise Release Branches documentation</a>. For details on the hardened i=
mages, refer to the <a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/ai-enterprise/planni=
ng-resource/ai-software-regulated-environments-white-paper/latest/index.htm=
l" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>AI Software for Regulated Environments White Pa=
per</strong></a>.<br><br><br></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>.You're receiving this email because you are a part of an NGC =
Organization with access to NVIDIA AI Enterprise and have subscribed to Ann=
ouncement notifications."<br>To unsubscribe, sign in to your NGC organizati=
on and update your notification <a href=3D"https://org.ngc.nvidia.com/accou=
nt" rel=3D"nofollow">settings</a>.<br><br>
